Having some event to handle? use raw TR and TD instead

```html
<Table fields="{ fields }">
	{#list dataSource as ds}
	<TR>
		<TD>{ ds.name }</TD>
		<TD>{ ds.email }</TD>
		<TD>
			<Button primary sm on-click="{ this.onClick( ds ) }">Modify</Button>
		</TD>
	</TR>
	{/list}
</Table>
```

